  FTB++
  
  This package contains some tools to merge (and convert into utf-8), revise 
  the XML structure and extend the content of the Paris 7 French Treebank [1]
  Corpus.
  
  Has been tested on 
  	ftb-v120101/corpus-tagged
  	Sequoia v3.3 [2]
  	
  With
  	java version "1.6.0_24"
	OpenJDK Runtime Environment (IcedTea6 1.11.5) (6b24-1.11.5-0ubuntu1~12.04.1)
	OpenJDK 64-Bit Server VM (build 20.0-b12, mixed mode)
	16 Go RAM
  
  on Ubuntu 12.04 with n a computer with 16 Go of RAM (you may need less)
  [1] http://www.llf.cnrs.fr/Gens/Abeille/French-Treebank-fr.php
  [2] https://www.rocq.inria.fr/alpage-wiki/tiki-index.php?page=CorpusSequoia
  
  
QUICKSTART
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
  1) Download on
    https://sites.google.com/site/nicolashernandez/resources
  
  2) Un-archive and get the root directory
    export PACKAGEVERSION=ftb++-v20130205
    tar -xvzf $PACKAGEVERSION.tar.gz
    cd $PACKAGEVERSION
  
  3) Run the whole process (merge, revise and extend) by typing
  	chmod u+rx ftb++.sh
    ./ftb++.sh merge+revise+extend -i /Path/To/The/FrenchTreebank/corpus-tagged -o /tmp/ftb-merged-revised-extended.xml
  
  
